---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Programs" currentPath="/programs">
  <div class="section-nav">
    <a href="/programs" class="active">Programs Overview</a>
    <a href="/programs/free-first-consultation">Free Consultation</a>
    <a href="/programs/the-splint">Splints I Use</a>
    <a href="/programs/program-option-1">Program Option 1</a>
    <a href="/programs/program-option-2">Program Option 2</a>
    <a href="/programs/coping-without-retraining">Coping Options</a>
  </div>

  <article>
    <h1>Retraining Programs & Support</h1>
    <p>I offer several options to help musicians retrain their motor control, manage symptoms, and design orthotics to bypass focal hand dystonia blocks.</p>
    
    <h2>Options & Resources</h2>
    <div class="card-grid">
      <a href="/programs/free-first-consultation" class="card">
        <h3>Free First Consultation</h3>
        <p>A introductory Skype session to assess your symptoms and discuss how a retraining program can help you.</p>
      </a>
      
      <a href="/programs/the-splint" class="card">
        <h3>Splints I Use</h3>
        <p>Learn about how physical orthotic splints are constructed and used to isolate movement during retraining.</p>
      </a>
      
      <a href="/programs/program-option-1" class="card">
        <h3>Program Option 1</h3>
        <p>A guided retraining program focusing on basic movement isolation and motor map retraining.</p>
      </a>
      
      <a href="/programs/program-option-2" class="card">
        <h3>Program Option 2</h3>
        <p>A comprehensive coaching option with frequent video feedback and dynamic exercise adjustments.</p>
      </a>
      
      <a href="/programs/coping-without-retraining" class="card">
        <h3>Coping Without Retraining</h3>
        <p>Strategies, instrument modifications, and ergonomic changes to help you continue playing while managing FHD symptoms.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
